    <string name="settings_privacy_title">Privacy policy</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_last_updated">Last updated: April 23, 2026</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_1_title">1. Information we collect</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_1_content">We collect information you provide directly, such as your name, email, business details, and your clients and events data. We also automatically collect information about how you use the app to improve our services and keep the platform secure.</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_2_title">2. How we use information</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_2_content">We use collected information to:
• Provide and improve our services
• Manage your account and subscription
• Send important notifications about events and payments
• Process payments securely
• Comply with legal and regulatory obligations</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_3_title">3. Data storage</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_3_content">Your data is stored securely on servers with industry-grade encryption. We implement technical and organizational security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration.</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_4_title">4. Sharing information</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_4_content">We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for advertising purposes. We only share data with essential service providers (payments, infrastructure) or when required by law.</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_5_title">5. Your rights and deletion</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_5_content">You have the right to access, correct, and request deletion of your personal data. To exercise your deletion right, you can start the process from account settings or visit our public deletion page:
creapolis.dev/delete-account</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_delete_account_cta">Go to account deletion page</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_6_title">6. Cookies and similar technologies</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_6_content">We use secure local storage to keep your session active and remember your preferences. We do not use tracking technologies for commercial purposes or share browsing behavior.</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_7_title">7. Changes to this policy</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_7_content">We may update this policy occasionally to reflect changes in the service or legal requirements. We will notify you of significant changes through the app or by email.</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_8_title">8. Contact</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_section_8_content">If you have questions about this privacy policy or how your data is handled, contact us at:
hola@creapolis.dev</string>
